	<div class="brief">
		<div class="content-grid">
			<div class="brief-box">
				<div class="brief-text">A large media company asked us to design an innovative video player experience for their new online streaming service. They needed a solution that not only gave users access to their favorite content, but also helped them discover something new.</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

