		<div class="content-grid">
			<div class="outputs-row">
				 <div class="output-item medium">
					<img src="images/wave-final-ui-1.png">
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="caption"><em>Simple controls</em></p>
			<p class="caption">We wanted the watching experience to be as easy as possible, keeping the controls simple, and making the most out of our lean-back, veg-out, catch-up-on that-latest-blockbuster experience. Big play/pause button on hover makes interruptions much easier...especially with popcorn hands.</p>
		</div>
