				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="caption"><em>Binge behavior</em></p>
			<p class="caption">Watching online usually means one thing, binging. We wanted to make access to the next episode as easy as possible or recommend something new if they finished their favorite show.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="outputs">
		<div class="content-grid">
			<div class="outputs-row">
				 <div class="output-item medium">
